          "type": "text",
          "text": "USP_BillingGroupAvailableByInvoiceRetrieve",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " is designed to retrieve billing group information associated with a specific invoice from a SQL Server database. It takes an invoice ID as input and optionally filters by billing type. The procedure logs its execution details, including any exceptions, and can trigger an email notification if an error occurs."
